name: Actions of a child
description:
My son decided to save over my work with a video of him playing with a self constructed exploding orb that he was controlling. 

with that said i can not snap my fingers an go back to my piece, i must start again thats ok it was my fault for having not saved it prior, that said i thought it might be cool to mint still, so i am all proceeds from sales will go to him and his artistic creative little cheeky mind, Tweet him a msg on my Twitter @bighootez | Jamison is his name..
